{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 469.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I think I know where he is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they said, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said then, to this girlfriend, 10 minutes on the corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I went there, and we get-- to get over a small bush-- it's about this high-- from the [INAUDIBLE] to our house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we crawled on our belly-- you know, like this-- through those bushes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the man who was interrogating was sitting at the window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It looked straight to that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Jan, who was, well, allowed to see us, was sitting with his back to it, was just the wrong way around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we had to crawl on our belly and did that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then with our hands, we grabbed the thing, and we took those things out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave them to her, and I said, you must come in 10 or 20 minutes, and act very [PANTING] you know, like you have been or have made a long bicycle trip, and tell that your brother had it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, the brother disappeared, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we played it that way, and that worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what happened to the package?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took the stamps out and gave them to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home, with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but they didn't know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never-- we-- they were very young, yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were young people in that time, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's long ago.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- we had-- we had an-- a coal bin, with a false bottom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could-- I have a picture of that coal bin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- he-- you could go in there and then there was a long slough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've never been in it myself, but my husband has been in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
